-- Dr. Johanna de Boer - English-Speaking General Practitioner
('Dr. Johanna de Boer', 'Doctors', 'Highly-rated English-speaking family medicine physician serving the international community in Madrid. Born in the Netherlands and raised in Sweden, Dr. de Boer studied medicine in Prague and completed her Family Medicine residency in Madrid. Fluent in English, Spanish, Dutch, and Swedish with 6 years of experience. Offers in-person consultations in Alcobendas, online/video consultations worldwide, and home visits throughout the Madrid area. Specializes in primary care, pediatric illnesses, infections, chronic disease management (hypertension, diabetes), and trauma-related issues. Known for patient-centered care with perfect English fluency and 5-star rating from 394+ verified reviews. Works with Spanish electronic prescription system (REMPe) valid at all pharmacies in Spain.', 'Calle del Marqués de la Valdavia', 'Alcobendas', 'Madrid', NULL, NULL, 'https://internationaldoctor.eu/', true, true, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
